<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>I need more details also.....I just happened to walk into befallen at lvl 31 to help someone get their corpse for them, and ran into the guy.  He was a blue con, so i killed him.....although he did take 3 bubs of life from me...but it only took 3 wrath's to kill him.  Now that i have the icon, i need to know what else i need for the quest.  None of these EQ sites show any info for this quest.<BR>
